<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Apex Grid Series — Spring Oval Challenge</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07090d;
      --bg-soft: #0d1118;
      --panel: rgba(14, 18, 26, 0.9);
      --panel-2: rgba(20, 24, 34, 0.95);
      --line: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      --text: #f5f7fb;
      --muted: #a7b0c0;
      --accent: #ff4f2f;
      --accent-2: #ff9b4a;
      --green: #6ee7a8;
      --shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.42);
      --radius: 24px;
      --radius-sm: 16px;
      --max: 1240px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255, 79, 47, 0.14), transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(255, 155, 74, 0.1), transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #0b0e14 0%, #07090d 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 42px 42px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.45), rgba(255,255,255,0.06));
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
    button { font: inherit; }

    .container,
    .nav-inner,
    .topbar-inner {
      width: min(var(--max), calc(100% - 32px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(8, 10, 14, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
    }

    .topbar-inner {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 10px 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .chip-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255, 79, 47, 0.55);
    }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(7, 9, 13, 0.84);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 18px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      min-width: 200px;
    }

    .brand-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 1000;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .brand-title span { color: var(--accent); }

    .brand-sub {
      margin-top: 4px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-weight: 650;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .btn {
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      font-weight: 850;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.18s ease, opacity 0.18s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-primary {
      color: white;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(255, 79, 47, 0.28);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--text);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    main.container { padding-bottom: 40px; }

    section { padding: 18px 0; }

    .hero {
      padding-top: 34px;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .glass {
      background: var(--panel);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-radius: 28px;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding: 34px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(255, 79, 47, 0.12), transparent 34%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.012)),
        var(--panel);
    }

    .hero-copy::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -10% 18% 40%;
      height: 220px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.07), transparent);
      transform: rotate(-10deg);
      filter: blur(10px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 9px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: #ffd6c6;
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    h1, h2, h3, h4 { margin: 0; line-height: 1.05; }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.7rem, 5vw, 5.3rem);
      font-weight: 1000;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 10ch;
    }

    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #ffffff 35%, #ff9c4b 68%, #ff4f2f 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      background-clip: text;
      color: transparent;
    }

    .lead {
      margin: 18px 0 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.07rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
      max-width: 62ch;
    }

    .stat-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .stat-card,
    .feature-card,
    .info-card,
    .rule-item,
    .faq-item,
    .footer-card,
    .timeline-step,
    .progress-box,
    .form-wrap {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.035);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      border-radius: 18px;
    }

    .stat-card {
      padding: 16px;
    }

    .stat-card small,
    .meta-item small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .stat-card strong,
    .meta-item strong {
      font-size: 1.12rem;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .prize-panel {
      overflow: hidden;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 85% 18%, rgba(255,155,74,0.14), transparent 22%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.015)),
        var(--panel-2);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .prize-head {
      padding: 26px 26px 0;
    }

    .prize-label {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .prize-title {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 1000;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 0.95;
    }

    .prize-image-wrap {
      margin: 22px 26px 14px;
      min-height: 310px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      background:
        linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 79, 47, 0.16), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), rgba(255,255,255,0.015)),
        #0d1118;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 28px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .prize-image-wrap::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 25% 28%, rgba(255,255,255,0.12), transparent 0 14%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 78% 30%, rgba(255,79,47,0.22), transparent 0 17%),
        linear-gradient(115deg, transparent 16%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 19%, transparent 22%, transparent 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 53%, transparent 56%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .prize-image {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      max-height: 250px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 22px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.45));
    }

    .prize-meta {
      padding: 0 26px 26px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .meta-item {
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: end;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 1000;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 62ch;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .panel {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .feature-grid,
    .info-grid,
    .faq-grid,
    .footer-grid,
    .rule-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .info-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .faq-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr 0.85fr; }
    .rule-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }

    .feature-card,
    .info-card,
    .rule-item,
    .faq-item,
    .footer-card {
      padding: 22px;
    }

    .feature-card h3,
    .info-card h3,
    .footer-card h3,
    .form-title,
    .timeline-title {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .feature-card p,
    .info-card p,
    .rule-item,
    .faq-item p,
    .footer-card p,
    .footer-card a,
    .timeline-note,
    .form-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .info-card strong {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      font-weight: 950;
    }

    .rule-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .register-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .timeline,
    .form-panel {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .timeline-steps {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .timeline-step {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 46px 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .step-num {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(255,79,47,0.22);
    }

    .timeline-step h4 {
      margin: 0 0 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .progress-box {
      padding: 18px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .progress-head {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .progress-head strong {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .progress-head span {
      color: var(--green);
      font-weight: 850;
    }

    .progress-bar {
      height: 14px;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 999px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .progress-fill {
      height: 100%;
      width: 76%;
      border-radius: inherit;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
      box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(255,79,47,0.35);
    }

    .form-wrap {
      padding: 22px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    form {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .field-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 750;
      color: #dbe2ee;
    }

    input,
    select,
    textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px 15px;
      font: inherit;
      outline: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }

    input::placeholder,
    textarea::placeholder { color: #8fa0ba; }

    input:focus,
    select:focus,
    textarea:focus {
      border-color: rgba(255,155,74,0.6);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,155,74,0.12);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 108px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    .checkbox {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .checkbox input {
      width: 18px;
      height: 18px;
      margin-top: 2px;
      accent-color: var(--accent);
    }

    .link-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .link-list a { color: var(--muted); }
    .link-list a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .footer-bottom {
      padding: 24px 0 10px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1080px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .register-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .info-grid,
      .faq-grid,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .footer-grid > :first-child {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav-inner,
      .section-head,
      .footer-bottom,
      .progress-head,
      .topbar-inner {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .register-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .info-grid,
      .faq-grid,
      .footer-grid,
      .field-row,
      .stat-grid,
      .prize-meta,
      .rule-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-copy,
      .prize-panel,
      .panel,
      .timeline,
      .form-panel {
        padding-left: 18px;
        padding-right: 18px;
      }

      .prize-image-wrap {
        margin-left: 0;
        margin-right: 0;
      }

      h1 { max-width: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-inner">
      <div class="chip"><span class="chip-dot"></span> Spring Oval Challenge registration now open</div>
      <div class="chip">25 driver cap · Structured race control · Prize-backed event</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-title">Apex <span>Grid</span> Series</div>
        <div class="brand-sub">Competitive Sim Racing</div>
      </div>

      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#home">Home</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#event">Event</a>
        <a href="#rules">Rules</a>
        <a href="#register">Register</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#register">Register Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy glass">
          <div class="eyebrow"><span class="chip-dot"></span> Seasonal Special Event</div>
          <h1><span class="gradient-text">Sim Racing Competition</span></h1>
          <p class="lead">
            Apex Grid Series returns with a full-distance oval event built for disciplined drivers, clean racecraft, and serious pace. Compete in Forza Motorsport (2023) at Eaglerock Oval over 200 laps for a chance to take the grand prize.
          </p>

          <div class="stat-grid">
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Race Date</small>
              <strong>17 March</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Track</small>
              <strong>Eaglerock Oval</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Race Length</small>
              <strong>200 Laps</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Platform</small>
              <strong>Forza Motorsport 2023</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Grid Status</small>
              <strong>19 / 25 Registered</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-card">
              <small>Entry</small>
              <strong>Free Registration</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#register">Secure Your Slot</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#rules">View Sporting Rules</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="prize-panel glass">
          <div class="prize-head">
            <div class="prize-label">Grand Prize</div>
            <div class="prize-title">Moza R3<br>Bundle</div>
          </div>

          <div class="prize-image-wrap">
            <img src="moza.png" alt="Moza R3 Bundle" class="prize-image">
          </div>

          <div class="prize-meta">
            <div class="meta-item stat-card">
              <small>Check-In</small>
              <strong>7:00 PM</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item stat-card">
              <small>Race Start</small>
              <strong>8:00 PM</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item stat-card">
              <small>Format</small>
              <strong>Season Event</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-item stat-card">
              <small>Availability</small>
              <strong>6 Spots Remaining</strong>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>About Apex Grid Series</h2>
        <p>
          Apex Grid Series is a structured sim racing competition format focused on organized race nights, stewarded sessions, clean driving expectations, and limited-grid events designed to feel professional from registration through results review.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="panel glass">
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Established Event Format</h3>
            <p>Built around seasonal specials, fixed-cap grids, published rules, and a consistent race control structure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Clean Racing Standard</h3>
            <p>Drivers are expected to maintain discipline through traffic, restarts, lane changes, and contact management.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Broadcast-Ready Presentation</h3>
            <p>Event pages, timing windows, and check-in procedures are formatted to feel like a legitimate competitive series.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3>Prize-Backed Competition</h3>
            <p>The winning driver takes the featured hardware reward after final result verification and steward review.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="event">
      <div class="section-head">
        <h2>Event Details</h2>
        <p>
          This round is an endurance-style oval challenge designed to reward consistency, focus, pit discipline, and traffic management over a long green-flag distance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="panel glass">
        <div class="info-grid">
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Venue</h3>
            <p>Official competition track selection for this event.</p>
            <strong>Eaglerock Oval</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Title</h3>
            <p>Main championship special event format.</p>
            <strong>Spring Oval Challenge</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Game</h3>
            <p>Event platform used for race night.</p>
            <strong>Forza Motorsport (2023)</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Distance</h3>
            <p>Total race length for the main event.</p>
            <strong>200 Laps</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Entry Cap</h3>
            <p>Limited field to preserve session quality.</p>
            <strong>25 Drivers</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="info-card">
            <h3>Prize</h3>
            <p>Winner reward after official classification.</p>
            <strong>Moza R3 Bundle</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
